OL,3,CTata Steel starts voluntary redundancy
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FTata Steel has begun asking employees
OL,7,Fif they would consider voluntary
OL,8,Fredundancy, according to the UK
OL,9,Fgovernment following a meeting of its
OL,10,Ftransition board.
OL,12,FTata has asked employees to express
OL,13,Finterest in the process which will run
OL,14,Funtil 7 August.
OL,16,FUK government ministers are conducting
OL,17,Ftalks with the steel giant's
OL,18,Frepresentatives to try and save as
OL,19,Fmany of the 2,800 at-risk-jobs as
OL,20,Fpossible.
