OL,3,CTata Steel starts voluntary redundancy
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FThe company is set to close the second
OL,7,Fof its Port Talbot blast furnaces in
OL,8,FSeptember due to accumulating losses
OL,9,Fof #1m a day.
OL,11,FPlans are in place to build an
OL,12,Felectric arc furnace at the Port
OL,13,FTalbot site, which will be able to
OL,14,Fproduce greener steel.
OL,16,FTata Steel says it has ambitions to
OL,17,Fproduce net-zero steel by 2045 in the
OL,18,FUK "at the latest" and plans to
OL,19,Freduced 30% of its CO2 emissions by
OL,20,F2030.
