OL,3,CTata Steel starts voluntary redundancy
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FOn Thursday, 11 July, recently-
OL,7,Fappointed Labour Welsh Secretary Jo
OL,8,FStevens conducted her first meeting as
OL,9,Fchair of the Tata Steel transition
OL,10,Fboard.
OL,12,FIt was set up by the previous
OL,13,FConservative UK government to support
OL,14,Fpeople and businesses affected by the
OL,15,Fplans, and includes representatives of
OL,16,Fbusinesses, unions, the Welsh
OL,17,Fgovernment and local politicians.
