OL,3,CTata Steel starts voluntary redundancy
OL,4,Cprocess
OL,6,FWelsh Secretary Jo Stevens has
OL,7,Fcommissioned a 'rapid assessment' of
OL,8,Fhow immediate support can be offered
OL,9,Fto those affected.
OL,11,FShe said: "This Government is
OL,12,Fdetermined to do all it can to protect
OL,13,Four Welsh steel industry and has
OL,14,Fimmediately reset our approach on how
OL,15,Fwe work with businesses and
OL,16,Fcommunities. We will work
OL,17,Fcollaboratively with a single focus to
OL,18,Fsupport our steel industry and
OL,19,Faffected communities.
